"$:/plugins/JorisL/Texify/readme": {
    "created": "20260314214007053",
    "text": "; Texify
Plugin to let (certain) tidlers look and feel more like a LaTeX document.

; Settings

{{$:/plugins/JorisL/Texify/settings/settings}}

; Usage

Set CSS selector setting to filter the tiddlers that this style should be applied on.
Examples:

* Apply style on all tiddlers with tag "tex" or "Journal": `[data-tags~="tex"],[data-tags~="Journal"]`
* Apply style on all tiddlers except for system tiddlers or tiddlers tagged "Attachment": `.tc-tiddler-frame:not(.tc-tiddler-system):not(.tc-tagged-Attachment)`

Set font family, size, maximum text width according to personal preference.

; Source

* [[Demo page|https://jorisl.github.io/TiddlyWiki-Plugins/]]
* [[Repository|https://github.com/JorisL/TiddlyWiki-Plugins]]",
